data.text:
The Sky Sport Breakers will be looking for another slam-dunk performance at NPDC’s TSB Stadium when they take on the Perth Wildcats in January 2023.

The team heads back to New Plymouth on for what promises to be a great family night out.

This is a high-energy, family-friendly and exciting basketball experience.

We have seating and packages to suit everyone. There are corporate deals available to treat your clients through to family discounts. Don’t miss out on this amazing sporting event.
